text: Yuika, do you have a moment?

I wanted you to see the design of the
new costumes I mentioned the other day.
Oh! I'd love to see them!

Wow... They have such a refreshing design...
And the feather motifs are a nice touch.

I see...
It's perfect for 283 Production!

That's great...!
It seems like you really like it.

Of course!
I can't wait for everyone to wear them together.

Once the costumes arrive,
you'll get to try them on too, so look forward to it.
